<br>
Your account can be compromised through no action or inaction of your own.  Reasons are simple:<br>
<br>
Remember the whineplay forums?  And the technical forums for when you had client trouble?  Remember them posting your login ID not your chat handle?  Well that is a first step, half of what you need to login as some one else.<br>
<br>
Run a trace route to Verant's EQ servers.  Sorry don't hape IPs handy for ya.  Notice how it hits about 6 maybe more stops on the way?  Packet sniffers can snag your data and later pull your login info out.  Don't even think about encryption, if it was so easy and good what Verant is using you think ShowEQ would be around still?<br>
<br>
Now I am by no means a hacker, even if I had the programming skills to do it I wouldn't.  Before you ask why some one would go to the trouble, think about the jerks out there with time and skill to do it.  They do it to piss people off and make their lives miserable. <p><br>
